<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-10 ">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell wrapper" style="" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" data-w="12">

<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-11 ">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-rich_text heading wow fadeInUp" style="" data-widget-type="rich_text" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<div class="cell-wrapper layout-widget-wrapper">
<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1517229163958500" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: none;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><h2>PERINATAL MOOD AND ANXIETY DISORDERS THE MAIN DIAGNOSES</h2>
<p><span style="visibility: visible; animation-name: none;">The term Perinatal Mood and Anxiety Disorders is used to encompass Depression in the pre-partum (before), antepartum (during) and postpartum (after) periods and affects approximately 1 in 7 women for each pregnancy experience.&nbsp; While "Postpartum Depression" is the most known, "postpartum" in fact means "after pregnancy."&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></span>
</div><!--end layout-widget-wrapper -->
</div><!--end widget-span -->
</div><!--end row-->
</div><!--end row-wrapper -->

<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-12 ">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-widget_container three-col-adjust" style="" data-widget-type="widget_container" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1517233068453527" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget_container hs_cos_wrapper_type_widget_container" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget_container" data-hs-cos-type="widget_container"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729042" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell bg-img-title-text-cm align-center all-text-white" style="background-image:url(https://www.wildermanfund.org/hubfs/Assets%202018/depression.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;border-radius:4px;">
    <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            
            <div class="text-mod">
                 <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
                    <div class="row-fluid">
                        <h5>DEPRESSION</h5>
<p>One of several mental illnesses affecting 20% of mothers during and/or after pregnancy.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="/depression"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #ffff99;">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

</div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729043" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell bg-img-title-text-cm align-center all-text-white" style="background-image:url(https://www.wildermanfund.org/hubfs/175545935.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;border-radius:4px;">
    <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            
            <div class="text-mod">
                 <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
                    <div class="row-fluid">
                        <h5>ANXIETY</h5>
<p><span>Postpartum Anxiety affects more than 10% of pregnant and postpartum women. Racing, intrusive thoughts are common and can worsen if untreated.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span><a href="/anxiety"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #ffff99;">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></span></p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

</div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729044" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell bg-img-title-text-cm align-center all-text-white" style="background-image:url(https://www.wildermanfund.org/hubfs/Assets%202018/shutterstock_169647155.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;border-radius:4px;">
    <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            
            <div class="text-mod">
                 <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
                    <div class="row-fluid">
                        <h5>OBSESSIVE COMPULSIVE DISORDER (OCD)</h5>
<p>Symptoms are common, but unwanted and repetitive. Intrusive thoughts and behaviors interfere with daily life and functioning.</p>
<p><a href="/obsessive-compulsive-disorder-ocd?hs_preview=ZWcerZJC-5730495147"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #ffff99;">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

</div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729052" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell bg-img-title-text-cm align-center all-text-white" style="background-image:url(https://www.wildermanfund.org/hubfs/Assets%202018/shutterstock_83231545.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;border-radius:4px;">
    <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            
            <div class="text-mod">
                 <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
                    <div class="row-fluid">
                        <h5>POST-TRAUMATIC STRESS DISORDER (PTSD)</h5>
<p>Resulting from real and perceived Perinatal trauma, PTSD is a debilitating illness affecting over 10% of women and partners.</p>
<p><a href="/post-traumatic-stress-disorder-ptsd"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #ffff99;">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

</div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729053" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell bg-img-title-text-cm align-center all-text-white" style="background-image:url();background-size:cover;background-position:center center;border-radius:4px;">
    <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            
            <div class="text-mod">
                 <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
                    <div class="row-fluid">
                        <h5>POSTPARTUM PSYCHOSIS</h5>
<p><span>The most rare diagnosis affecting 0.1% - 0.2% of postpartum women, usually&nbsp;within the first 2 weeks.</span></p>
<p><span><a href="/postpartum-psychosis"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #ffff99;">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></span></p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

</div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729054" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell bg-img-title-text-cm align-center all-text-white" style="background-image:url(https://www.wildermanfund.org/hubfs/Assets%202018/176157090.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center center;border-radius:4px;">
    <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            
            <div class="text-mod">
                 <div class="row-fluid-wrapper">
                    <div class="row-fluid">
                        <h5>BIPOLAR (BPD) AND MOOD DISORDERS</h5>
<p><span>A Bipolar or Mood Disorder is characterized by periods of extreme highs (hypomania/mania) and lows (depression).</span></p>
<p><span><a href="/postpartum-psychosis-0"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; color: #ffff99;">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></strong></a></span></p>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

</div></span>
</div><!--end widget-span -->
