<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-21 ">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-widget_container " style="visibility: visible; animation-name: none;" data-widget-type="widget_container" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1517559760287125" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget_container hs_cos_wrapper_type_widget_container" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget_container" data-hs-cos-type="widget_container"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729055" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 testimonial_cm">


<div class="testimony-text span12">
    <blockquote>More women will suffer from postpartum depression and related illnesses in a year than the combined number of new cases for men and women of tuberculosis, leukemia, multiple sclerosis, Parkinson's disease, Alzheimer's disease, lupus and epilepsy."</blockquote>
</div>

<div class="span12 below-quote-mod">
    <div class="testimony-img span4" style="background-image:url('');background-size:cover;background-position:top center;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:100%;"></div>
    <div class="span8 about-testimony">
    <h5>Postpartum Progress</h5>
    <h5>FACT</h5>
    </div>
</div>


</div></div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729056" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: none;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 testimonial_cm">


<div class="testimony-text span12">
    <blockquote><span>OB/GYNs need to be there to reassure mothers that whatever they're feelingâ€”whatever 'bad' thoughts they're havingâ€”are normal. You're not a bad mom because you're dealing with mental health issues."</span></blockquote>
</div>

<div class="span12 below-quote-mod">
    <div class="testimony-img span4" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: none;background-image:url('https://www.wildermanfund.org/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202018-04-05%20at%205.07.43%20PM.png');background-size:cover;background-position:top center;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:100%;"></div>
    <div class="span8 about-testimony">
    <h5>Jamie Zahlaway-Belsito, National Advocacy Chair, The National Coaltion for Maternal Mental Health</h5>
    <h5>Testimonial</h5>
    </div>
</div>


</div></div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729057" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: none;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 testimonial_cm">


<div class="testimony-text span12">
    <blockquote>Despite the frequency of depression among new mothers, large numbers of affected individuals may not be identified as having a treatable condition, and only 15% obtain professional care."</blockquote>
</div>

<div class="span12 below-quote-mod">
    <div class="testimony-img span4" style="background-image:url('');background-size:cover;background-position:top center;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:100%;"></div>
    <div class="span8 about-testimony">
    <h5>Harvard Center on the Developing Child</h5>
    <h5>FACT</h5>
    </div>
</div>


</div></div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729058" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 testimonial_cm">


<div class="testimony-text span12">
    <blockquote>Women during their childbearing years account for the largest group of Americans with depression."</blockquote>
</div>

<div class="span12 below-quote-mod">
    <div class="testimony-img span4" style="background-image:url('');background-size:cover;background-position:top center;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:100%;"></div>
    <div class="span8 about-testimony">
    <h5>American College of Obstetricians &amp; Gynecologists</h5>
    <h5>FACT</h5>
    </div>
</div>


</div></div>
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_5556729059" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_custom_widget" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="custom_widget"><div class="span12 testimonial_cm">


<div class="testimony-text span12">
    <blockquote><span>Women who suffer from depression during pregnancy and their infants are at risk for costly complications.&nbsp; Nearly $15 billion dollars is spent on childbirth-related hospitalizations and half of these costs are billed to private insurance."</span></blockquote>
</div>

<div class="span12 below-quote-mod">
    <div class="testimony-img span4" style="background-image:url('');background-size:cover;background-position:top center;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:100%;"></div>
    <div class="span8 about-testimony">
    <h5>National Business Group on Health</h5>
    <h5>FACT</h5>
    </div>
</div>


</div></div></span>
</div><!--end widget-span -->
